item.title:
♻️ Reusable cups ♻️
When you buy a drink you’ll be charged £1 for a reusable cup for the weekend. Hold onto your cup, and use it every time you buy a drink from one of our bars. Please return your cup to a bar or our cup bins before you leave.
Cheers! 🍻
#TimberFestival
